# Title: Verclsid.exe Runs COM Object
# Author: Victor Sergeev, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-09
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects when verclsid.exe is used to run COM object via GUID
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1218
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_verclsid_runs_com.yml

CommandLine="*/S*" CommandLine="*/C*" Image="*\\verclsid.exe" OR OriginalFileName="verclsid.exe" NOT (CommandLine="*verclsid.exe\" /S /C {*" CommandLine="*} /I {*" ParentImage="*C:\\Windows\\System32\\RuntimeBroker.exe")